docs.lead_paragraph: PHILADELPHIA, July 18. -- Harry K. Thaw reached Philadelphia at 6 o'clock this evening and went to the Bellevue Stratford Hotel, where quarters had been engaged for him by his secretary, H.J. Rice. He expects to start for Pittsburgh tomorrow morning at 8:40 o'clock.

headline.main: THAW REACHES PHILADELPHIA; Runs from Crowd in Station -- Issues Another Statement.
